Built-in requests:
  1. POST /api/auth/login
    => call config.authentication.onAuth(payload) => userData
    => create JWT
    => send 403 or 200 OK with JWT

  2. POST /api/auth/introspect
    => GET user data from JWT
    => call config.authentication.checkAuth(userData) => boolean
    => send 401 OR 200 with:
      - active: boolean
      - exp: timestamp
      - userData: any

Built-in decorators:
  1. @AuthenticatedRequest()
  2. @UseMiddleware(middleware: (req, res, next) => any!?)
    e.g. @UseMiddleware(checkRole('ADMIN'))
